             was indicted for <rs id="t18281204-127-off666" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18281204-127-off666" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18281204-127-off666" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18281204-127-cd667" type="crimeDate">20th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18281204-127-off666 t18281204-127-cd667"></join>, 1 watch, value 10s.; 1 chain, value 3s.; 2 seals, value 10s.; 1 key, value 5s., and 3 sovereigns
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18281204-127-victim1108" type="victimName">
                     Robert 
                     Brows
                  <interp inst="t18281204-127-victim1108" type="surname" value="Brows"></interp>
